original_title: Die Autokannibalen - Wir klauen nur das Beste!
overview: Jochen and his brother Alexander, called "The Car Cannibals," really only steal the best: Ferraris and Porsches. Their ancestors in the Wild West were horse thieves and shot their way out of trouble. Can the love of a woman set them on the right path?
title: Die Autokannibalen - Wir klauen nur das Beste!
